Hi Stefan,
I record EVP maker at 75% speed setting. I record direct to the 
computer with a Soundblaser Audigy card set to +3 octave to bring the 
pitch back, this is why it sounds a bit &#39;off&#39;. The &quot;Ohhh Yes&quot; clip is 
just how it was recorded, I find it most unusual. I&#39;ll try more 
testing tonight, it&#39;s been exciting.

Dave
